room_title: Escape room "Tahoe '64" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
review: We've successfully escaped from the Tahoe '64 Room and the Chain Reaction Room. We enjoyed the Tahoe Room better because of the creative unique props and puzzles and the use of local lore. We've played over 20 rooms, and we rank the Tahoe Room near the top. Chain Reaction was also fun, but more stressful, with a buttload of puzzles and lots of red herring props. Hope to return to try their other rooms. Highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Tahoe '64" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
review: Amazing! We have done a few escape rooms and the Tahoe '64 is now a top for us. It was great to have a room with some local vibes! We highly recommend it! Can't wait to do the next one!

room_title: Escape room "Tahoe '64" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
review: We escaped Tahoe 64 at Key and Code in Sparks, Nevada. This is the best escape room we have done. I loved the variety and creativity that was there. Can't wait to try the others out there. The people working were the best. Thanks.
